1	// Pure utility module (audit A47): dependency-free helpers used everywhere.
2	// Pulled out of the monolithic app.js as a first ESM split — others can follow
3	// (auth.js, grids.js, setup.js, workspace.js) once a frontend test harness is
4	// in place to catch regressions.
